item.description:
@peoplereaper2 wrote:

its either in client.java or player.java find out your current home coordinates and search the first part of the cord (the x cord) in client or player untill you find the cords of your current home area and change that then do the same for the home tele or home tele command which is in client.java and change that the shops are in npc.cfg change there cords to get them out of varrok and put the ones you want in varrok to make a seperate shop for donators you should make a ::donator command to tele you to a donator area and put the shop there
